        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Coordinating and Leveraging Activities for School Security Act or the CLASS Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill establishes in the Department of Homeland Security a council to ensure the coordination of activities, plans, and policies to enhance the security of schools and preschools against acts of terrorism.</p>]]></text>
